<h2>Help Center</h2>
<p>Need assistance? Here's how we can help:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Buying Insurance:</strong> Go to <em>Buy Insurance</em>, select your vehicle type, enter details, choose a plan, and make payment.</li>
    <li><strong>Renewing Insurance:</strong> Click <em>Renew Insurance</em>, enter your old policy number, and proceed with payment.</li>
    <li><strong>Claiming Insurance:</strong> Use the <em>Claim Insurance</em> link, specify your reason, and contact our support team.</li>
    <li><strong>Estimate Premium:</strong> Use the <em>Estimate Insurance</em> tool to calculate your expected premium before buying.</li>
</ul>

<p>If you're still stuck, visit our <a href="/Home/FAQ">FAQ</a> or reach out via the <a href="/Home/Contact">Contact</a> page.</p>
